rComments: Carolina is one of the best professors I have ever had throughout my educational career. She is an extremely talented professor and she makes class very fun and worth attending!!! There is a lot of homework, but they are all simple worksheets. Awesome professor that I would recommend to anybody looking to improve their Spanish/learn the language.

Carolina is awesome. She is super helpful in class, and during her office hours she will spend time to make sure that her students fully understand the content of the class. She is really enthusiastic about teaching. This is a class that students enjoy attending.

Profesora Castillo is a wonderful teacher. She is very energetic, funny, and helpful during her lectures. She aims to engage everyone in the learning process and has us do a good amount of group activities. I would highly recommend taking her class. Also, her tests are easy and exactly what you learn during class.
Carolina is a super nice professor and she cares about her students. She uses the workbook pretty much everyday in class.
Carolina is the best spanish teacher I have ever had. She is very lively, engaging and obviously loves teaching. I would take any class she is teaching!

Profesora Carolina is the best! She has so much energy, good sense of humor, and she comes prepared to every lecture with powerpoints, activities, games (board games, charades, etc.). Her tests are also very fair and simple. If you do your Quia, participate in class, and review the vocab, you will easily get an A.
